org.tensorflow.op.core

Class TensorListConcat<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.tensorflow.op.PrimitiveOp
      • org.tensorflow.op.core.TensorListConcat<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - data type for tensor() output
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Op

    @Operator
public final class TensorListConcat<T>
extends PrimitiveOp
    Concats all tensors in the list along the 0th dimension.

    Requires that all tensors have the same shape except the first dimension.

    input_handle: The input list. tensor: The concated result. lengths: Output tensor containing sizes of the 0th dimension of tensors in the list, used for computing the gradient.
